rows.label: bf04390150_0020
rows.name:
Hm? Oh, if it isn't Nia. Yoshitsune did
mention you had turned traitor.

rows.label: bf04390150_0050
rows.name:
Of all the lowlifes Bahn could have
made a deal with...

rows.label: bf04390150_0060
rows.name:
Lowlifes? Coming from the traitorous rookie?
You should watch your words...

rows.label: bf04390150_0070
rows.name:
Don't mind her, Benkei. Not when we
are standing before the Holy Grail herself!

rows.label: bf04390150_0080
rows.name: Ah, truly the heavens must have blessed us that we-

rows.label: bf04390150_0110
rows.name:
The traitor, we kill.
The Holy Grail, we retrieve. Got it?

rows.label: bf04390150_0120
rows.name: It's a pain, but that's the mission.

rows.label: bf04390150_0140
rows.name: Hikari and Nia... They are my friends and comrades.

rows.label: bf04390150_0145
rows.name: I'm not letting you touch them!
